long_description: Use your iPhone 5s in and around water in ways you never dreamed! The light, thin LifeProof Nuud Case preserves clarity and direct touch while remaining completely waterproof without a screen cover. Nuud protects your iPhone 5s from drops, dirt and dunks while keeping the touchscreen uncovered for direct touch; case seals onto screen, creating a waterproof design. Smart design allows full access to every feature, button, control and port, including full compatibility with the iPhone 5s Touch ID function. The slim, clear LifeProof Nuud Case for iPhone 5s highlights the sleek, brilliant design of the iPhone 5s. Anti-reflective optical-glass lens for crystal clear photography; speaker ports deliver maximum sound output and clarity. Waterproof, shockproof, dirt-proof and snow-proof design is submersible to 6.6 ft. (2m), survives drops from 6.6 ft. (2m) and totally seals out dirt, dust and snow.
